    "updated_at": "2016-07-02T03:34:38Z",
    "body": "This is an upstream bug of Chromium, it seems to have bugs on drawing canvas, I created a Chrome app and the canvas does not even show in it:\n[dialog-element.zip](https://github.com/electron/electron/files/344391/dialog-element.zip)\n\nI'm closing this since we are not able to fix it on Electron's side, I suggest reporting this to Chromium's issues list instead.\n"
